    "level": "ONET",
    "difficulty": "medium",
    "type": "multiple-choice",
    "content": {
      "text": "โดเมนของฟังก์ชัน $f(x) = \\sqrt{x - 2}$ คือข้อใด",
      "choices": {
        "a": "$x > 2$",
        "b": "$x \\geq 2$",
        "c": "$x < 2$",
        "d": "$x \\leq 2$",
        "e": "$x \\in \\mathbb{R}$"
      }
    },
    "answer": "b",
    "hint": "นิพจน์ภายในรากที่สองต้องมีค่าไม่ติดลบ",
    "solution": {
      "steps": [
        "สำหรับ $\\sqrt{x-2}$ จะมีความหมายเมื่อ $x - 2 \\geq 0$",
        "$x - 2 \\geq 0$",
        "$x \\geq 2$"
      ]
    },
    "tags": ["domain", "square-root"],
    "source": "ONET 2566"
  },
  {
    "id": "rf-003",
    "topicId": "relations-functions",
    "subtopic": "composition",
    "level": "A-Level",
    "difficulty": "medium",
    "type": "multiple-choice",
    "content": {
      "text": "กำหนดให้ $f(x) = x^2 - 4$ และ $g(x) = x + 1$ จงหา $f(g(2))$",
      "choices": {
        "a": "3",
        "b": "0",
        "c": "9",
        "d": "-1",
        "e": "5"
      }
    },
    "answer": "e",
    "hint": "หา $g(2)$ ก่อน แล้วแทนผลลัพธ์ใน $f$",
    "solution": {
      "steps": [
        "หา $g(2) = 2 + 1 = 3$",
        "หา $f(g(2)) = f(3) = 3^2 - 4 = 9 - 4 = 5$"
      ]
    },
    "tags": ["composition"],
    "source": "A-Level 2566"
  },
  {
    "id": "rf-004",
    "topicId": "relations-functions",
    "subtopic": "inverse-function",
    "level": "A-Level",
    "difficulty": "medium",
    "type": "multiple-choice",
    "content": {
      "text": "ฟังก์ชันผกผันของ $f(x) = 3x - 6$ คือข้อใด",
      "choices": {
        "a": "$f^{-1}(x) = \\dfrac{x+6}{3}$",
        "b": "$f^{-1}(x) = \\dfrac{x-6}{3}$",
        "c": "$f^{-1}(x) = 3x + 6$",
        "d": "$f^{-1}(x) = \\dfrac{1}{3x-6}$",
        "e": "$f^{-1}(x) = \\dfrac{x}{3} + 6$"
      }
    },
    "answer": "a",
    "hint": "ให้ $y = 3x - 6$ แล้วแก้สมการหา $x$ ในรูปของ $y$",
    "solution": {
      "steps": [
        "ให้ $y = 3x - 6$",
        "$y + 6 = 3x$",
        "$x = \\dfrac{y+6}{3}$",
        "ดังนั้น $f^{-1}(x) = \\dfrac{x+6}{3}$"
      ]
    },
    "tags": ["inverse-function"],
    "source": "A-Level 2565"
  },
  {
    "id": "rf-005",
    "topicId": "relations-functions",
    "subtopic": "types-of-functions",
    "level": "ONET",
    "difficulty": "easy",
    "type": "multiple-choice",
    "content": {
      "text": "ฟังก์ชันใดต่อไปนี้เป็นฟังก์ชันหนึ่งต่อหนึ่ง (one-to-one)",
      "choices": {
        "a": "$f(x) = x^2$",
        "b": "$f(x) = |x|$",
        "c": "$f(x) = 2x + 1$",
        "d": "$f(x) = \\sin x$",
        "e": "$f(x) = x^2 - 4$"
      }
    },
    "answer": "c",
    "hint": "ฟังก์ชันหนึ่งต่อหนึ่งคือฟังก์ชันที่ค่า $x$ ต่างกันให้ $f(x)$ ต่างกันเสมอ",
    "solution": {
      "steps": [
        "$f(x) = 2x + 1$ เป็นฟังก์ชันเชิงเส้น",
        "ถ้า $f(x_1) = f(x_2)$ แล้ว $2x_1 + 1 = 2x_2 + 1$, ดังนั้น $x_1 = x_2$",
        "จึงเป็นฟังก์ชันหนึ่งต่อหนึ่ง",
        "ส่วนฟังก์ชัน $x^2$ และ $|x|$ ไม่ใช่ เพราะ $f(-1) = f(1)$"
      ]
    },
    "tags": ["one-to-one", "types-of-functions"],
    "source": "ONET 2566"
  }
]
